Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.25,0:00:04.72,Default,staff,0000,0000,0000,,Once we bag this up, we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:05.48,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.00,Default,worker A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go make that report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:14.53,Default,worker B,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.00,Default,worker A,0000,0000,0000,,Sure finished early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:16.99,Default,worker B,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.12,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now. Shall we see \Nwhat this fellow is made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.80,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Komari, I see you caught the scent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:35.78,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, though. The first sip \Nfrom this faucet goes to—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:39.47,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnTimes New Roman\fscx90\b1\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\c&H090F0F&\pos(152,293.333)}Literature Club
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.47,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:43.11,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You'll see. Just hurry up and open the d-door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:43.93,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.37,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu! Push harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.83,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I-It won't close!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:01.96,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:03.59,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:13.46,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me out! I-I-I'm still trapped inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.09,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs16\fnGeorgia\b1\c&H1F2520&\pos(314.667,49.333)\frz342}You are \N\h\hthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:16.30,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. S-Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.90,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs16\fnGeorgia\b1\c&H1F2520&\pos(314.667,49.333)\frz342}You are \N\h\hthe pen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.32,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,So I get that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.98,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,you're dressed like that as a \Ncostume fitting for the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:59.37,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,but what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:07.08,Default,Shikiya,0000,0000,0000,,Literature club. Your exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:10.75,Default,Shikiya,0000,0000,0000,,application is... very lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:16.46,Default,Shikiya,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to tell her, but she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.18,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs14\b1\fnGeorgia\fscx80\pos(360,69.333)\c&H34434A&\frz348.3}Tsuwabuki Festival Application for Classroom Use
