Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.18,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\b1\fax-0.15\fnGeorgia\fscx90\shad0\fs7\c&H444339&\pos(377.333,232.667)\frz344.7}\h\h\h\hThe deadline is 10/5!\N\h\h\h\hI can wait until after class.\N\h\h\hIf there's something you want\N\h\h\hthe student council to do\N\h\hbefore the actual Tsuwabuki\N\h\hFest, tell us.\N\hIf you don't understand\N\hsomething or have any questions,\N\hcome see the student council.\N\NShikiya Yumeko
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.18,Default,Shikiya,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do it right, you get rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.63,Default,Shikiya,0000,0000,0000,,That okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.51,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:34.05,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,W-We'll do it right. \NI want to get a lot of visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:39.11,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for leaving you with \Nall that Tsuwabuki Fest prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.32,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.46,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, \NKomari's more into it than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.10,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:50.36,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to talk to you \Nabout the next club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:54.29,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Koto and I have entrance exams, \Nso we're quitting after Tsuwabuki Fest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:58.79,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,And we were thinking of asking Komari-chan \Nto be the next club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:03:59.84,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Komari?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:05.00,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And we want you to be\Nvice president to back Komari-chan up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.30,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.81,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But I can tell you're really \Nworried about Komari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.74,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:18.25,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're graduating and leaving \NKomari-chan here all alone! I'm so, so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.88,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should stay one \Nmore year just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:24.11,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Koto, that sounds too real coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:28.90,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu-kun, for this year's Tsuwabuki Fest,\N we'll stay in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:33.00,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,We thought letting Komari-chan do the prep \Nand stuff would boost her confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.79,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,So please keep an eye on Komari-chan \Nfor me. Be nice to her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.21,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, to the best of my ability—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:43.30,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,She likes pudding more than ice cream. \NAnd she doesn't drink coffee, so watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:47.51,Default,Koto,0000,0000,0000,,She also doesn't love the green parts of \Ngreen onions, so chop those finely, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.89,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember that if \NI ever make her pork soup.
