Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.76,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, dear brother, \Nhow are things going these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.44,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,These days? Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:09.87,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,The cafeteria sink was removed, and the \Nplumbing for the faucets was changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.24,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the faucets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:16.18,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And I was able to confirm \Njust how the flavor had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.42,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't that just lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:23.38,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, you just received \Na message from Yanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:26.88,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,"Lunch tomorrow at the fire escape stairs."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.24,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Kaju...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:31.30,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at my \Nphone without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:35.39,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,But big brother, you always act \Nso indifferent toward Yanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.60,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,As your little sister, \NI need to supervise your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.60,Top,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.08,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs12\3c&HF2E7DD&\c&H575C5F&\frz349.4\pos(233.333,249.333)}Looking forward to it.
