Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.44,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs9\3c&HF2E7DD&\c&H615449&\frz348\pos(388.667,28)}PM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.44,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs14\3c&HF2E7DD&\c&H477D63&\frz351.4\pos(452.667,14.666)}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.44,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs12\3c&HF2E7DD&\c&H5B5D51&\frz349.4\pos(239.333,91.333)}Lunch tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.44,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs11\3c&HF2E7DD&\c&H5B5D51&\frz349.4\pos(234.667,140.667)}at the fire escape stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.44,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs9\3c&HF2E7DD&\c&H615449&\frz348\pos(352,166.667)}PM
