Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.44,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs12\3c&HF2E7DD&\c&H477D63&\pos(377.333,247.333)\frz350.6}Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.44,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.90,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Now you should be able to make some progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.83,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to make you a very nice lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:55.75,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Nukumizu-kun, don't get the wrong idea. \NIt isn't about me holding a grudge this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:59.27,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,As a friend—no, as a \Nrepresentative of all humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.87,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I simply felt the need to raise an objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:07.05,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, our class has started preparations \Nfor Tsuwabuki Fest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.55,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,"Halloween on the Corner," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:13.39,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So I went to the nurse's office \Nto take costume measurements...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:18.44,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,And even though Sosuke was there, \NKaren-chan started taking off her clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.62,Flashback Top,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:22.94,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course the girl in charge of wardrobe \Nnoticed and kicked Sosuke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.00,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,But then, Sosuke said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.54,Flashback,Sosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Bad habit! I'm just so used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:36.34,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yanami-san, if any of this \Nlooks good, want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.86,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Anything I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:43.22,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Help yourself. \NThe Scotch egg is a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.92,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Looks good! Then I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:51.25,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone pick the \Nrice ball in a situation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.35,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You said I could take anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:07:00.75,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, changing the subject a little, \Ndo you have any ideas for the lit club's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:04.19,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. What did Komari-chan say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.78,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,She said if we're doing it, \Nshe wants people to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:11.28,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,She really wants the lit club's plan \Nto succeed, so she's working super hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:15.66,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Komari-chan really\N is a girly girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.08,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,A girly girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.09,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the third-years are \Nall leaving the club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:24.88,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Even if her crush doesn't return her feelings,\N she wants to send him off with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:28.18,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You go, Komari-chan. She's so innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.29,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.64,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she's doing, Nukumizu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.56,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I can get behind that. And Komari-chan's \Ngonna be the next president, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.32,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What, you already knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:44.43,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukinoki-senpai sent me a message saying, \N"Keep an eye on Komari-chan for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:48.25,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,So I spent a lot of time brainstorming \Nby myself. Wanna hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.82,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.05,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,People are drawn to food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.66,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:00.20,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But that has nothing to do with the lit club.\NPlus, there aren't many of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:05.20,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,In which case we should give the exhibit \Na theme that has to do with food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.84,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's grab Komari-chan and get researching!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.72,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind doing research, but why here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.68,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:21.56,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs6.5\fnComic Sans MS\b0\c&HAD9C83&\move(71,67,83,67)}For the Love \Nof Drink
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:21.56,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs14\fnComic Sans MS\b1\c&HAD9C83&\move(72,80,84,80)}Yasuko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:21.56,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,This area is a fusion of things old and new.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.27,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,The community also has a long \Nhistory of artistic innovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.53,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:32.11,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm saying we should let \Nthe environment here inspire us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:36.65,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,so that we start to feel it... and stuff? \NYou know, like that. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.44,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like she hasn't \Nthought about it very deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.64,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.25,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:45.48,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why did you guys ask me to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:50.00,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you were having trouble deciding \Non a theme for Tsuwabuki Fest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.26,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We thought this might give you ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.58,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,B-But aren't I getting in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.22,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,In my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.92,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, you're going out with Yanami, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.02,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.33,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you even think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.31,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys are a-always doing stuff together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.44,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\shad0\fs10\b1\blur0.3\pos(513.333,114)\c&H636051&\3c&H97927A&}Sea Otter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.80,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Komari. Otters are cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.74,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Otters? L-Like, the sea creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:21.45,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The otter. \NThose little guys sure look cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:31.55,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\shad0\fs22\b1\blur0.3\c&H636051&\3c&H97927A&\move(378,126,345,120)\frz6.235\t(\fscx120\fscy120)}Sea Otter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:25.37,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,and they eat more than 20% \Nof their body weight each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.52,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Otters are cute. They're big eaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:31.55,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't make you \Nfall in love with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.67,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's essentially what I'm getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.84,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:40.39,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come over here! \NI found a shop that looks interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.39,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\fs15\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\c&H534764&\pos(500,21)}Toyohashi Bldg. Shopping Arcade
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.38,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a matcha framboise, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.89,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You, Komari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.91,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.23,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:00.45,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Here. It looks bad, but I haven't touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.54,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:07.00,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're here for research. \NIsn't it best if we all eat some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.96,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, o-okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.15,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:21.93,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,but I kinda get the feeling you'd treat me \Na little differently if I was out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.60,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,If we assume that's true, \Nwould you like me to explain why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.68,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.31,Top,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.91,Top,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}are{\i0} you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.55,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.44,Top,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.55,Top,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Ah! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.02,Top,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs11\fax0.17\b1\fnGeorgia\fscx80\c&H2F3334&\frz351.1\pos(296,123.999)\frx0\fry4}Tsuwabuki Festiv{\c&H34434A&}al Application for Classroom Use
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs7\fax0.01\b0\fnArial\fscx90\c&H34434A&\frz349.1\pos(366.667,143.333)}Month
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs6.5\fax0.01\b0\fnArial\fscx90\c&H34434A&\frz351.1\pos(396,147.334)}Day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\an1\fs8\b1\fax0.2\fnArial\fscx88\c&H353B3D&\frz351.3\pos(206.666,129.334)}Please fill out th{\c&H34434A&}e information below\N\h{\c&H353B3D&}to apply to b{\c&H34434A&}orrow a classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs11\fax0.17\b1\fnGeorgia\fscx80\c&H2F3334&\frz351.1\frx0\fry4\pos(275.333,191.333)}Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs10\fax0.17\b1\fnGeorgia\fscx80\c&H2F3334&\frz351.1\frx0\fry4\pos(384,187)}Applicant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\an1\fs8\b1\fax0.2\fnArial\fscx88\c&H353B3D&\frz351.3\pos(322.667,186)}Class
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\an1\fs8\b1\fax0.2\fnArial\fscx88\c&H353B3D&\frz351.3\pos(318.667,210.667)}Name
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs8\fax0.17\b1\fnGeorgia\fscx80\c&H0B1316&\frx0\fry4\frz352.1\pos(207.333,210.666)}Exhi{\c&H2F3334&}bit Contents
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs10\fax0.17\b1\fnGeorgia\fscx80\c&H25353C&\frx0\fry4\frz352.1\pos(238.667,346.667)}Floor Plan
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.55,0:10:37.86,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,So I summarized the conversation Komari \Nand I had after we went out yesterday.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.56,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to hear your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.41,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't part of that conversation, was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.95,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,So she did notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.49,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't want the distraction, \Nso we left Yanami out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:54.46,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we'd like you to perform \Na different kind of job, Yanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:58.20,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, we have a role in mind \Nwe think only you are capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.59,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Something only I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:04.85,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's basically \Nsomething like a consultant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.06,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling you'd be perfect for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:11.23,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Consultant? You mean you're going\N to consult with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:15.32,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why you had to \Nshorten it like that, but that is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.88,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That sounds like \Nsomething I could work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.95,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I'd be perfect for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.16,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, back to the main point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:27.82,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to use your idea and run \Nwith the theme of food and literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:32.20,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We could showcase authors' favorite foods \Nor foods that appear in their books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.33,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Then put those foods in our exhibit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:38.84,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We could list classic recipes and show \Nphotographic representations in the exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.05,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Photographic representations?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.03,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we going to be serving actual food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.05,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we aren't doing a restaurant—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.51,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Attention please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.95,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.61,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,When I said I wanted to use food as the theme,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:55.59,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,this is not what I meant at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.79,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then what did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:02.57,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't you picture Showa-era authors \Neating beef hot pot and eel and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:07.33,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the literature club, so we've gotta\N try to feel that same literary spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.97,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,This girl was planning on putting out\N a beef hot pot at the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.79,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,You know we aren't allowed \Nto cook in the classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.01,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,And the deadline for club \Nrestaurants has already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:19.05,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just come up with the ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:22.53,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who has to find a way \Nto make them happen, Nukumizu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.26,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We picked the wrong person to consult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:29.97,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I-It says here that b-baked sweets\N and snacks are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.93,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\bord0\shad0\b1\an8\fs10\fsp5\c&H0D1E26&\pos(380,4.667)}Cooking Room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:37.40,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,My friend in the cooking club said we can \Ncook in here as long as we clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.71,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,So what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.44,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's already passing the buck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.91,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know any recipes, Yanami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:48.00,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I know how to make fried dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.26,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.69,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,You fry flour mixed with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.99,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,The key to enjoying it is emptying\Nyour mind of all desire while eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:57.04,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to eat such a depressing snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.47,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:06.59,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Komari, you seem used to this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:11.89,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've got some rugrats at home. \NI'm a-always making snacks for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:15.48,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just have to match this \Nwith the theme of our exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.02,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:21.40,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yakishio is in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.95,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.87,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya! Whatcha up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.33,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon-chan! We just finished \Nbaking some cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.71,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.21,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, these are really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.82,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. I do all right sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.52,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Komari's the one who made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.29,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Feminine charm off the charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:47.59,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I haven't been able to help \Nwith the festival stuff at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.81,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You have track practice, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.71,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,We nee-uh hi anuh-huh uhb-aye-buh hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:59.38,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we need to find a new club advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.51,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,She was able to decipher that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:05.42,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, advisor? You mean the \Nlit club doesn't have an advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.18,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there were problems \Nand she quit a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.53,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't turn in applications \Nwithout an advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:16.84,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukinoki-senpai told me we \Nhad to go find someone new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.75,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say that sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:22.72,Default,Anna,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should pick a teacher \Nwe know really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.72,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,All the teachers I know are from track.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.89,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.25,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:37.36,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's you guys? The hell you doin' 'ere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:37.89,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:38.44,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.20,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hell. Go take care of that at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.85,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not whatever you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.86,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to ask you for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.08,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,You came here together to ask for my advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:53.18,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,No! Hurry up and go to the nurse's office!\N Konuki-chan can help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.67,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:58.23,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Amana-chan, you gotta \Nbecome the lit club's adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.79,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what's all this about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:05.17,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I apologize. The literature club \Nwe're in doesn't have a faculty advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:08.82,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find a teacher to become\Nour advisor before Tsuwabuki Fest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.59,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please, Amana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:15.06,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,A-ha. Well, if that's the problem, \NI sure would like to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:18.06,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm already an advisor \Nfor the ping pong club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.39,Default,Lemon,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:25.18,Default,Amanatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Just leave it to me! \NI'll figure somethin' out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs40\b1\blur0.4\pos(238,154)\c&H39312E&}Toyo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs16\b1\blur0.4\c&H39312E&\pos(240,266)}Roadside Market
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.03,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs16\b1\blur0.4\c&H39312E&\pos(240,303)}Toyohashi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.99,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord0\shad0\b1\fax-0.07\fs9\fscx80\c&H273645&\frz348.8\pos(312,154.666)}For Adults
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.99,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord0\shad0\b1\fax-0.07\fs12\fscx80\c&H273645&\frz348.8\pos(307.333,180.667)}First Love Lemon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:32.99,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,First love lemon for adults, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.75,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Here, big brother. Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.42,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? \NApparently, it uses local quail eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.50,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Mm. S'good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:48.46,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs30\fay0.24\fscx90\b1\blur0.4\c&H6E7877&\pos(226,81.333)\frx0\fry10}Toyo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:48.46,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs14\fscx90\fax-0.01\fay0.08\b1\blur0.4\c&H39312E&\pos(226.666,184)\frx0\fry14}Roadside Market
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:48.46,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs14\fscx90\fax-0.01\fay0.03\b1\blur0.4\c&H39312E&\frx0\fry14\pos(227.333,222.667)}Toyohashi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:51.20,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, dear brother, why'd you suddenly\N want to visit the roadside market today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:56.05,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the lit club needs snacks to \Nput out for our Tsuwabuki Fest exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:16:00.19,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We also want to have a small area\N for people to sit and rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.38,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to come and look for ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.81,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.15,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,So it'll be a kind of roadside market\N at the school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.28,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,What snacks are you considering?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:14.53,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,There's a famous story about \Nhow Natsume Soseki loved peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.98,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,We could write a little explanation \Nabout it and sell them cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:21.50,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, Natsume Soseki\N had quite the sweet tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.21,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he indulged in sugar-coated peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:29.50,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar-coated, huh? But I'm not sure \Nwe can make something that fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:33.13,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,If that's troubling you, dear brother,\N your Kaju is here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.58,Default,Kaju,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the snack-making to me!
