Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:08.21,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,So we've decided on the topic of the \Nlit club exhibit for Tsuwabuki Fest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.42,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at the sheet provided.
