Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.85,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, which faucet would Komari \Nwant to drink from at this time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.90,Italics,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:12.14,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:16.99,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Our application for classroom use \Nneeds the club representative's signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.87,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.38,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.06,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.28,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm f-fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.36,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to overdo it. \NOur senpai are still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.82,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as much as you can—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.12,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,B-But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.52,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:01.02,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. See you after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.28,Default,Boy 1,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:26.61,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,According to my calculations, it takes 85 \Nseconds to get from here to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:30.08,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave one minute from now,\N we can still beat the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.54,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your calculations?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:37.54,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,It means we can wait here together \Na little longer until the crowd dies down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:47.07,Default,Komari,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm in a different class,\N so it's a little farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:50.15,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Then just walk there a bit quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:54.06,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.5\fs26\fnGeorgia\pos(320,75)\c&HE9E9E9&\t(0,400,\c&HB2B1B5&)\t(400,800,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(800,1200,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(1200,1600,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(1600,2000,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(2000,2400,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(2400,2800,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(2800,3200,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(3200,3600,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(3600,4000,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)}Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:54.06,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.5\fs25\an8\fnGeorgia\c&HE9E9E9&\t(0,400,\c&HB2B1B5&)\t(400,800,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(800,1200,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(1200,1600,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(1600,2000,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(2000,2400,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(2400,2800,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(2800,3200,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\t(3200,3600,\c&HB2B1B5&\blur0.3)\t(3600,4000,\c&HE9E9E9&\blur0.9)\pos(320,255)}If You Are In Trouble, Feel Free to Consult
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:27.28,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.4\fs26\fax-0.11\b1\frz6.341\c&H1E1C1B&\pos(305.334,126)}Student Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.91,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.12,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:36.23,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought the application form that \NShikiya-senpai asked us to correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:39.99,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Might you be one of those people \Nfrom the literature club?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.04,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs6\move(412,137,404,138.5)\c&H111514&}Tsuwabuki High School
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.04,Default,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\blur0.3\bord0\shad0\fs10\b1\c&H111514&\fscx95\move(425,179,418,181)}Basori Tiara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.25,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at my chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.46,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not try anything \Njust because we're alone in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:50.73,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I was just looking at your name tag!\N I wasn't sure how to read your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:53.46,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,It's Basori.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:55.20,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,And your given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:58.00,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Tiara!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:02.98,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem? Has my name\N inconvenienced you in some way?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:03.88,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:15.16,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,It seems quite lively today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:17.87,Default,Tiara,0000,0000,0000,,Chairwoman! It's so nice to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:20.22,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:24.20,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.09,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,So what brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:30.09,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, paperwork for the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:32.40,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Shikiya gave you corrections, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:34.30,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:37.39,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry. Your application is accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.62,Default,Nukumizu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:43.10,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,The third-years are leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:46.57,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,In Shikiya's presence, I had to \Nturn a blind eye to many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:49.29,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,But that will no longer be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:56.08,Default,Hibari,0000,0000,0000,,As a student of Tsuwabuki, you must \Nprepare yourself to live up to its reputation.